{
  "id": "6357b50ed56a690020533a10",
  "title": "恐れは逃げると倍になるが、立ち向かえば半分になる",
  "created": 1666692370,
  "updated": 1668770206,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6357b50ed56a690020533a10",
      "text": "恐れは逃げると倍になるが、立ち向かえば半分になる",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1666692370,
      "updated": 1666692370
    },
    {
      "id": "6357b512a9108b0000e86459",
      "text": "[ウィンストン・チャーチル]の言葉",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1666692370,
      "updated": 1666692379
    },
    {
      "id": "6357b514a9108b0000e8645a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1666692372,
      "updated": 1666692372
    },
    {
      "id": "6357b59fa9108b00004292e0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1666692511,
      "updated": 1666692511
    },
    {
      "id": "6357b597a9108b00004292de",
      "text": " [好きな言葉][あめみー.icon]",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1666692504,
      "updated": 1666693620
    },
    {
      "id": "6358f333a9108b000025b46b",
      "text": " \tちょっと関係ないけど、",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1666773811,
      "updated": 1666773818
    },
    {
      "id": "6358f250a9108b000025b466",
      "text": "  　[https://www.ntv.co.jp/toppa/articles/94ewlewwkgf6we8xr3.html 降り止まない落石…登山中のピンチから家族を守り抜いた作戦とは？｜THE突破ファイル｜日本テレビ]",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1666773584,
      "updated": 1666773819
    },
    {
      "id": "6358f2d1a9108b000025b469",
      "text": " 　\t落石から逃げずに家族を守ったストーリー",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1666773714,
      "updated": 1666773740
    },
    {
      "id": "6358f2eba9108b000025b46a",
      "text": " 　\t>お父さんを先頭に縦一列で並ぶことで幅を狭め、家族に落石が当たる危険を減らしつつ、落石が転がる方向をお父さんが見極め、一斉によけるという方法だ",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1666773740,
      "updated": 1666773886
    },
    {
      "id": "6358f257a9108b000025b467",
      "text": " 　番組は別だけど、ちょうどこんなストーリーを聞いたのと同時期に知った言葉",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1666773592,
      "updated": 1666773845
    },
    {
      "id": "6358f287a9108b000025b468",
      "text": " 　たとえ落石という[危険]が迫ったときでも「[恐れ]は逃げると倍になるが、立ち向かえば半分になる」のかと腑に落ちた記憶がある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666773639,
      "updated": 1666777033
    },
    {
      "id": "6358ff895e90c00000539c69",
      "text": " 　　この前の[登山で熊に遭遇]はこれに近そう[issac.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666776969,
      "updated": 1666777020
    },
    {
      "id": "6358ffca5e90c00000539c6b",
      "text": " 　　　[逆境ナイン]でも似たような話があったような",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666777035,
      "updated": 1666777059
    },
    {
      "id": "6357b59aa9108b00004292df",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5fb29108ce01660038a9108b",
      "created": 1666692506,
      "updated": 1666692506
    },
    {
      "id": "6357c77b5e90c00000258262",
      "text": " どういう文脈で言った言葉なんだろう？[issac.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666697084,
      "updated": 1666697101
    },
    {
      "id": "6357c7815e90c00000258263",
      "text": "　出典と原文が気になる[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1666697089,
      "updated": 1666697334
    },
    {
      "id": "6357c869e6003500006e3aa7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1666697322,
      "updated": 1666697322
    },
    {
      "id": "6357c9ca5e90c00000258270",
      "text": "出典はないが英文が載っていた[issac.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666697675,
      "updated": 1666697691
    },
    {
      "id": "6357c9ca5e90c00000258271",
      "text": " [https://estorypost.com/名言%E3%83%BB格言/winston-churchill-quotes-matome-jp-en/ ウィンストン・チャーチル名言まとめ（日本語、英語） - e-StoryPost]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666697675,
      "updated": 1666697692
    },
    {
      "id": "6357c9ce5e90c00000258273",
      "text": " >危険が迫った時、背中を向けて逃げ出すようではだめだ。かえって危険が２倍になる。しかし、決然として立ち向かえば、危険は半分に減る。何事に出会っても決して逃げ出すな。決して！",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666697678,
      "updated": 1666697699
    },
    {
      "id": "6357c9e25e90c00000258274",
      "text": " > One ought never to turn one’s back on a threatened danger and try to run away from it. If you do that, you will double the danger. But if you meet it promptly and without flinching, you will reduce the danger by half. Never run away from anything. Never!",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666697699,
      "updated": 1666697699
    },
    {
      "id": "63766344e5172d0000bf1557",
      "text": "  主観的な恐れではなく客観的な危険？[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1668703045,
      "updated": 1668703280
    },
    {
      "id": "6357c9cb5e90c00000258272",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666697675,
      "updated": 1666697675
    },
    {
      "id": "637642fd5b98c200005e1b0d",
      "text": " >金を失うのは小さく、名誉を失うのは大きい。しかし、勇気を失うことはすべてを失う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1668694781,
      "updated": 1668694841
    },
    {
      "id": "6376431f5b98c200005e1b0e",
      "text": " >Money lost -- little lost. ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1668694815,
      "updated": 1668694841
    },
    {
      "id": "6376431f5b98c200005e1b0f",
      "text": " >Honour lost -- much lost. ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1668694815,
      "updated": 1668694841
    },
    {
      "id": "6376431f5b98c200005e1b10",
      "text": " >Pluck lost -- all lost.",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1668694815,
      "updated": 1668694841
    },
    {
      "id": "637643305b98c200005e1b11",
      "text": "　かっこいいし、いかにもチャーチルが言いそうな言葉だけど、[実は言ってない名言]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1668694832,
      "updated": 1668695275
    },
    {
      "id": "6376434b5b98c200005e1b12",
      "text": "　言ったのは別の人らしい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1668694859,
      "updated": 1668694971
    },
    {
      "id": "637646645e90c00000091d64",
      "text": " 　E・W・ホーナングのYoung Bloodという作品で検索に引っかかった",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695643,
      "updated": 1668695827
    },
    {
      "id": "637647295e90c00000091d67",
      "text": "  　1898年初版",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695841,
      "updated": 1668695847
    },
    {
      "id": "6376471c5e90c00000091d65",
      "text": "  　[https://www.gutenberg.org/cache/epub/42902/pg42902-images.html Young Blood, by E. W. Hornung—A Project Gutenberg eBook]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695827,
      "updated": 1668695839
    },
    {
      "id": "6376475b5e90c00000091d78",
      "text": "  　Chapter 4 THE NEW HOME 最終部",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695891,
      "updated": 1668696017
    },
    {
      "id": "637647285e90c00000091d66",
      "text": "    >\"Well, my boy?\"",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695839,
      "updated": 1668695887
    },
    {
      "id": "637647425e90c00000091d69",
      "text": "    > \"It came back to me just now. It puts all that we have been saying in a nutshell. May I tell you, mother?\"",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695865,
      "updated": 1668695887
    },
    {
      "id": "637647425e90c00000091d6b",
      "text": "    > \"I am waiting to hear.\"",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695865,
      "updated": 1668695887
    },
    {
      "id": "637647425e90c00000091d6d",
      "text": "    > \"'Money lost—little lost.'\"",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695865,
      "updated": 1668695916
    },
    {
      "id": "637647425e90c00000091d6f",
      "text": "    > \"It's easy to say that.\"",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695865,
      "updated": 1668695887
    },
    {
      "id": "637647425e90c00000091d71",
      "text": "    > \"'Honour lost—much lost.'\"",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695865,
      "updated": 1668695887
    },
    {
      "id": "637647425e90c00000091d73",
      "text": "    > \"I call it everything.\"",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695865,
      "updated": 1668695887
    },
    {
      "id": "637647425e90c00000091d75",
      "text": "    > \"No, mother, wait! 'Pluck lost—all lost!' It's only pluck that's everything. We must never lose that, mother, we must never lose that!\"",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695865,
      "updated": 1668695887
    },
    {
      "id": "637647425e90c00000091d77",
      "text": "    > \"God grant we never may.\"",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695865,
      "updated": 1668695887
    },
    {
      "id": "637643aa5b98c200005e1b13",
      "text": "   Chapter 9 THE CITY OF LONDON",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668694954,
      "updated": 1668695968
    },
    {
      "id": "6376478d5e90c00000091d7a",
      "text": "    >That night he wrote it out on the back of a visiting card, and tacked the tiny text to the wall above his bed:—",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695940,
      "updated": 1668695942
    },
    {
      "id": "6376478f5e90c00000091d7b",
      "text": "    > ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695942,
      "updated": 1668695942
    },
    {
      "id": "6376478f5e90c00000091d7c",
      "text": "    > \"MONEY LOST—LITTLE LOST",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695942,
      "updated": 1668695942
    },
    {
      "id": "6376478f5e90c00000091d7d",
      "text": "    >  HONOUR LOST—MUCH LOST",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695942,
      "updated": 1668695947
    },
    {
      "id": "6376478f5e90c00000091d7e",
      "text": "    >  PLUCK LOST—ALL LOST.\"",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695942,
      "updated": 1668695947
    },
    {
      "id": "637647895e90c00000091d79",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668695937,
      "updated": 1668695937
    },
    {
      "id": "637656997c8c6d00005d0296",
      "text": "[逃げたら1つ、進めば2つ]",
      "userId": "6171231417617a001d7c8c6d",
      "created": 1668699802,
      "updated": 1668699842
    },
    {
      "id": "6376569e7c8c6d00005d0297",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6171231417617a001d7c8c6d",
      "created": 1668699806,
      "updated": 1668699806
    },
    {
      "id": "6376b44e7838e300004e4dd1",
      "text": "　わかるなあ[Mijinko_SD.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1668723792,
      "updated": 1668723798
    },
    {
      "id": "6376b4557838e300004e4dd3",
      "text": "　　不安や恐れってその対象をよく知らないほど膨れ上がる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1668723799,
      "updated": 1668723847
    },
    {
      "id": "6376b51e7838e300004e4dd5",
      "text": "　　　自分にどう降り掛かってくるかを予測しようとしても、形がわかっていないとあらゆる可能性が存在してしまっているので対処のしようがない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1668724000,
      "updated": 1668724092
    },
    {
      "id": "637736e71280f00000643a64",
      "text": "   [得体の知れない怪物]になって頭がおかしくなる[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1668757223,
      "updated": 1668757233
    },
    {
      "id": "6376b48e7838e300004e4dd4",
      "text": "　　立ち向かって仮に失敗しても、その失敗の大きさを正確に知ることができるし",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1668723855,
      "updated": 1668723997
    },
    {
      "id": "6376b44e7838e300004e4dd2",
      "text": "　「恐れは逃げると倍になるが、立ち向かえば半分になる」つまり[指数関数]？[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1668723792,
      "updated": 1668766676
    },
    {
      "id": "63775bd3e600350000dfad62",
      "text": " 　定式化が難しい気もするけれど、そのあたりは適当にやってみる",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1668766676,
      "updated": 1668766676
    },
    {
      "id": "63775bd3e600350000dfad63",
      "text": " 　まず「恐れ」の本体は無限遠点[$ +\\infty]にあるとして「恐怖関数」を[$ f(x)=2^{-x}]とおく",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1668766676,
      "updated": 1668766676
    },
    {
      "id": "63775bd3e600350000dfad64",
      "text": " 　　恐れを距離の関数とみており、[$ f(x)]は常に正の値をとる",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1668766676,
      "updated": 1668766676
    },
    {
      "id": "63775bd3e600350000dfad65",
      "text": " 　　　この話にはあまり関係ないけれど「負の恐怖」をうまく定義できるか？",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1668766676,
      "updated": 1668766676
    },
    {
      "id": "63775bd3e600350000dfad66",
      "text": " 　[$ x]軸上にいる太郎さん(仮名)が、初期値[$ x=0]から逃げる＝負の方向に1だけ進むと[$ f(-1)=2=2f(0)]となって、確かに恐怖が2倍である。同様に、立ち向かう＝正の方向に1だけ進むと[$ f(1)=\\tfrac{1}{2}=\\tfrac{1}{2}f(0)]となって、恐怖が半分になる",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1668766676,
      "updated": 1668766676
    },
    {
      "id": "63775bd3e600350000dfad67",
      "text": " 　これを[複素数]まで拡張できないか？",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1668766676,
      "updated": 1668766676
    },
    {
      "id": "63775bd3e600350000dfad68",
      "text": " 　　逃げもせず、立ち向かいもしない。すなわち恐怖に対して「横に進む」",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1668766676,
      "updated": 1668766676
    },
    {
      "id": "63775bd3e600350000dfad69",
      "text": " 　　しかしその場合「恐怖」が複素数値になってしまうので、ますます[意味不明]に...",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1668766676,
      "updated": 1668766714
    },
    {
      "id": "6377698f7838e3000006a94a",
      "text": " 　[その発想はなかった][Mijinko_SD.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1668770192,
      "updated": 1668770206
    },
    {
      "id": "637769967838e3000006a94b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1668770199,
      "updated": 1668770199
    }
  ]
}